text: Tetu may refer to: == Places == * Tetu Constituency, an electoral constituency in Kenya ** Tetu, Kenya, an administrative division in Nyeri County, Kenya * Tetu Lake, a lake of Ontario, Canada. == Other uses == * Têtu, a French gay magazine * a Marathi name for Oroxylum indicum * Tetu Nakamura, a Japanese film actor
title: Tetu
